text: Chan Kooi Chye (born 20 June 1921) is a Malaysian former sports shooter. He competed in the 50 metre rifle, prone event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1921 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Malaysian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Malaya Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Kuala Lumpur
